      • load

        public static Properties load(String resourceName)
                       throws IOException
        Load properties from the given resources using the current thread context class loader. The properties are expected to be encoded in UTF-8.
        Parameters:
        resourceName - The resource name
        Returns:
        The loaded properties, or null if the resource could not be found
        Throws:
        IOException - in case an error occurred while reading the properties

      • load

        public static Properties load(URL url)

        Load properties from the given URL. The properties are expected to be UTF-8 encoded.

        Note: this method does not set a read timeout!

        Parameters:
        url - the URL to load from
        Returns:
        The loaded properties
        Throws:
